# 🚀 Task Tracker Frontend

A modern, responsive Task Tracker UI built using React.js and Tailwind CSS. This frontend connects with a REST API backend to manage tasks efficiently.

---

## 📌 Features

- Add New Tasks
- Edit Tasks
- Delete Tasks
- View Task Statistics
- Search Tasks
- Filter by Status
- Sort Tasks (Newest, Oldest, A-Z, Z-A)
- Responsive UI (Mobile + Desktop)
- Real-time updates (without refresh)
- Clean dashboard UI

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- React.js (Vite)
- Tailwind CSS
- React Router DOM
- React Hot Toast
- Fetch API

---

